ing: 4 zucchini - peeled, sliced lengthwise, and sliced
des: "This is my favorite side dish that goes great with chicken or fish or served over rice or pasta."
ins: Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat; saute zucchini until softened, 5 to 10 minutes. Season zucchini with oregano and basil. Add tomato sauce; cook and stir until heated through, about 5 minutes. Sprinkle Parmesan cheese over zucchini mixture.
